snippet.title: Evercade - The Sydney Hunter Collection - Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sydney Hunter Collection brings together four great action-adventure titles from CollectorVision Games!

Available August 2023
Pre-order from June 1st 2023

Find out more:  https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/the-sydney-hunter-collection/

Full Games List:
Sydney Hunter and the Shrines of Peril
Sydney Hunter and the Sacred Tribe
Sydney Hunter and the Caverns of Death
Jester
